==Equipment and Endorsements==

Hadi is endorsed by Ignite Amps (Italy) and AMT Electronics (Russia).<ref>www.amtelectronics.com/artisty/hadi_sarieddine/</ref>

Hadi uses the following equipment:
*Ignite Amps TSB-1 Tyrant Screamer
* Schecter Guitars
*Ibanez Guitars
*AMT Electronics E-1, P-1, and B-1
*Line6
*Dunlop Guitar Picks
*D'addario Strings

